{"tid":1354152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家聽日唔好噓傑志","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:09:36.000Z","uid":207826,"like":268,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ee06f457c9ecf2479494a71cee1f44cbdeffd3d6","tid":1354152,"uid":207826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:43:58.000Z","msg":"我唔想聽日主隊比人噓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁搞到香港足球好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以留返港超先噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傑志聽日都係代表香港㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋會長都話同佢冇關係啦，求下大家唔好噓啦好唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地啲球員好多都係我地兄弟嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413a1f24f09476e61f652cf41d1cda530d37b00a","tid":1354152,"uid":6003,"like":10,"dislike":68,"score":-58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:46:02.000Z","msg":"我諗7年前都無人估到何君堯係咁鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c67db3dcf9df40f16aaa1ef97bd2e05c830846","tid":1354152,"uid":6003,"like":26,"dislike":11,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n當我求下睇開本地波既反傑黨<br />\n反少傑志兩日<br />\n留少兩日反傑comment<br />\n槍口對外先<br />\n你地無理由唔知條片係7年前<br />\n呢刻將矛頭指返入傑志唔見得對香港有著數"},{"pid":"298d0994d9bd6e72cbeb86595c36d74d84f0bae9","tid":1354152,"uid":1884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:5